Her palms are sweaty, knees weak, arms are heavy

Easy, no
Not like she did with the men in Benghazi,
And she’s scared, cause Trump’s close,
She knows that she’d be broke,
Without selling influence through that joke,
Of a foundation,gross!
So, she’s scared and Trump knows, that when he gets on that debate stage, that’s when it’s
Time to expose her lies, yo
This old gal’s gotta go
He better go capture this moment and hope it don't pass him
